name: **Illaunathowe**
description: Illaunathowe V511-589 Sheet 83 / Sheet 84 Triple headed grassy knoll in WNW Derrynane Harbour, an important roost as the only local isolated island grass. All other depicted islets locally are rocks. Attractive views of a splendid beauty spot. Land on shelves NE side or to taste. Launch from lovely beach at abandoned processing plant immediately to its W.
